{"title":"煤油灯","authors":["朱赤"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":11,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤油灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱赤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一灯如豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如一种朴素的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温暖简陋的窑洞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及窑洞外那棵枣树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一树红灿灿的果实香甜至今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一灯如豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀旧桌前一米八二的魁梧身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支毛笔蘸起暗红色光泽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过马兰纸涛声澎湃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目光睿智涌潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一双大手上羖羖飞动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一灯如豆，如一粒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如豆的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"植入茫茫夜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方，抽出鲜嫩的黎明……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}